title: Can't patch stuck at 33%
body:
Have tried it all, and have been through the whole google, re-install, repair tool, reset computer. I have even waited through another patch just to see if it works. Nothing works. Can some one tell me what to do? I miss playing league of legends, and want it to work on my computer.

Under is the report from patching

replies.body:
Issues at or after 33% during patching indicate that your patching is losing its connection to our patching servers. Our [**connection guide**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues) will walk you through configuring your network settings for League properly and should resolve this issue for you.

Let me know if it did!
